description:
Hayasaka Miku is the youngest member of the cast, starring as Dian Rayer (Iko Sue) on the "Cosprayers" show. She has a fear of heights which frequently causes problems during stunts.
Her name is derived from Hayasaka Ako (早坂アコ) of Choujin Sentai Jetman (鳥人戦隊ジェットマン) and Imamura Miku (今村みく) of Denji Sentai Megaranger (電磁戦隊メガレンジャー).
name: Hayasaka Miku
